egoe UI Emoji', 'Segoe UI Symbol';font-size:18px;font-weight:400;line-heigh=
t:29px;text-align:left;"><p style=3D"margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0"></p><p s=
tyle=3D"margin:10px 0">Huawei just said: =E2=80=9CShrinking transistors is =
running out of gas. Let=E2=80=99s stop wasting time on the roads instead.=
=E2=80=9D</p><p style=3D"margin:10px 0">The problem they=E2=80=99re attacki=
ng: In modern AI chips is a ton of time and power is lost not on actual cal=
culations, but on signals traveling long distances through wires between tr=
ansistors, memory, and other chips. Huawei calls this delay =CF=84 (tau).</=
p><p style=3D"margin:10px 0">Their fix =E2=80=93 LogicFolding: They =E2=80=
=9Cfold=E2=80=9D logic circuits vertically into layers so the most importan=
t paths become much shorter. Shorter roads =3D faster signals, less wasted =
energy, higher effective density.</p><p style=3D"margin:10px 0">Even on cra=
ppy old tech like 7nm-class processes they can hit 1.4nm-equivalent density=
 by 2031. </p><p style=3D"margin:10px 0">+55% transistor density, ~41% bett=
er power efficiency.</p><p style=3D"margin:10px 0">Already built 381 chips =
this way. First full version drops in new Kirin phone chips this fall.</p><=
h2>Why We Care? </h2><p style=3D"margin:10px 0">Sanctions blocked Huawei fr=
om TSMC=E2=80=99s best machines. So they made their own. It could potential=
ly weaken the moat of TSMC, Intel, and Nvidia. I will monitor carefully. </=
p><p style=3D"margin:10px 0">h.t Sanjay for the heads up</p><p style=3D"mar=
gin:10px 0"></p><p></p></div></td></tr>
